graph LR
    RHOAIOp[RHOAI Operator<br/>rhods-operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    RHOAIOp -->|cluster resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 1.28+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Conditional
    RHOAIOp -->|traffic mgmt, mTLS| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>CONDITIONAL<br/>Required for: KServe, ModelMesh]
    RHOAIOp -->|serverless autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving<br/>CONDITIONAL<br/>Required for: KServe]
    RHOAIOp -->|model auth| Authorino[Authorino<br/>CONDITIONAL<br/>Required for: model serving]
    RHOAIOp -->|external routes| OpenshiftRoute[OpenShift Route API<br/>CONDITIONAL<br/>Required on: OpenShift]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    RHOAIOp -.->|monitoring| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>Can deploy own stack]
    RHOAIOp -.->|certificates| CertManager[Cert Manager<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>Alternative: Service CA]

    %% Internal RHOAI Components Deployed
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI for workflows]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Jupyter notebooks]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| KServe[KServe<br/>Serverless serving]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>Multi-model serving]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow Pipelines]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>Distributed workloads]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| Ray[Ray Operator<br/>Ray clusters]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job queueing]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| Training[Training Operator<br/>Distributed training]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>AI explainability]
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| ModelReg[Model Registry<br/>Model versioning]

    %% Component Dependencies
    KServe -.->|requires| ServiceMesh
    KServe -.->|requires| Knative
    KServe -.->|auth| Authorino
    ModelMesh -.->|requires| ServiceMesh
    ModelMesh -.->|auth| Authorino

    %% Monitoring Stack
    RHOAIOp -->|deploys| MonitoringStack[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus, Alertmanager]
    MonitoringStack -->|scrapes| RHOAIOp
    MonitoringStack -->|scrapes| Dashboard
    MonitoringStack -->|scrapes| KServe
    MonitoringStack -->|scrapes| ModelMesh

    %% Platform Integration
    RHOAIOp -->|console links| OpenshiftConsole[OpenShift Console]
    RHOAIOp -->|manifest sources| GitRepos[Component Git Repos<br/>Build-time only]

